Violent Harvest (a letter)<br>
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br>
<br>
 *walks in quietly, hidden by her cloak, sets down a letter sealed by wax, and walks back out listening the the comotion around her*<br>
<br>
Violent Harvest,<br>
This letter is to those that I stood next to and fought by in Paw and Dreadlands. I thank you for the chance to fight by your side, learning more about you and the differences between us. It was nice for once, to see that the cleric and enchanter were not the ones to die. This letter is just a thank you, and if in the future you have an opening, I would be honored once again to join you.<br>
<br>
<br>
Sria Har`Graef<br>
45th Blind Enchantress of Marr<br>
Subject of Dark and Light<br>
Knights Templar <br>
 <br>
