 OOC: This letter is left on the door steps of your residence Sria, within Neriak. A copy is left within the guildhall as well for the Harvest.<br>
<br>
My dearest Sria,<br>
<br>
It is a shame that my business has kept me away from these gatherings that you have attended. I am glad to hear that you have allowed The Father back into your heart. I do so hope I read your letter correctly and you seek to become a seed and leave behind those fools within the knights.<br>
<br>
Speaking of which, I have not recieved any updates as to the completion of your 'test'. I do hope to hear from you soon.<br>
<br>
Shaede Wavecaller<br>
Harlot of Innoruuk<br>
<br>
