<br>
 Sria, I very much enjoyed your presence in paw with us. It was very nice to have a powerful enchanter on our side that night. You impressed me very much, as you have when I have fought by your side in the Great Divide. You have proven your worth to me as a killer and evoker of the mystic powers. It is a shame that you are not among our family more often. Others may denounce you for your beliefs but I welcome your skills at my side any day. I will beware your differences of which I do not understand, but I give equal respect to all who deserve it from me. Until the day comes when you prove me wrong, I hold you in the highest regards. Any lightborn who has the fearlessness to enter the camp of the enemy and fight along side of them in a dangerous dungeon earns the right to walk amongst me in battle. Be safe in your dark world and call upon me anytime you may need my assistance. <br>
<br>
Numadar The'Apocalypse<br>
Executioner of Hate<br>
